properties.Name: MineProcessingActivityAssetEventType
properties.Description:
A type of mine processing asset event related to the ore processing activity asset.

Ex:
- Output from process via asset (conveyor, pipe, pipeline etc.)
- Input to process via asset
- Asset Installation
- Asset Repair
- Asset Operation
- Asset Failure
